double getLag1Covariance()
Gets the lag-1 sample covariance of the unweighted observations. Note: See Box, Jenkins, Reinsel, Time Series Analysis, 3rd edition, Prentice-Hall, pg 31

Returns:
A double representing the sample covariance or Double.NaN if <=2 observations

getLag1Correlation
